## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

Weak passwords are one of the most common reasons for data breaches and cyber attacks.  
SecurePass solves this problem by providing:

- Real-time password strength analysis  
- Visual circular strength meter  
- Live security rules checklist  
- App-like, premium user interface  

This project is ideal for **BCA students**, **college mini projects**, **GitHub portfolios**, and **LinkedIn showcases**.

